<%-layout("/layouts/nav.ejs")%>
<body>
  <header class="privacy-banner">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Protecting your journey with GlobeTrek Adventures</p>
  </header>

  <main class="policy-container">
    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>1. Welcome</h2>
      <p>
        Thank you for choosing <strong>GlobeTrek Adventures</strong>. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your personal data while you explore, book, and travel with us.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Personal information (name, email, contact details).</li>
        <li>Booking and payment data handled securely via third-party gateways.</li>
        <li>Technical details like browser type and device information.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>3. Purpose of Data Usage</h2>
      <p>
        We use your data to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Confirm and manage your travel bookings.</li>
        <li>Personalize offers and provide support.</li>
        <li>Enhance website experience and customer satisfaction.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>4. Security Measures</h2>
      <p>
        Your information is stored securely using encrypted servers and restricted access. We comply with GDPR and other relevant data protection laws.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>5. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We only share essential information with travel partners (like hotels or airlines) required to complete your bookings. We do not sell your data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies help us analyze site usage and improve your browsing experience. You may disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You can request to access, modify, or delete your personal data anytime by emailing us at 
        <a href="mailto:privacy@globetrek.com">privacy@globetrek.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="policy-section">
      <h2>8. Updates</h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Any changes will be reflected here with a new revision date.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

